author: KATHY GANNON Associated Press
title: China sends medical aid to Pakistan to combat virus outbreak
description: Pakistan's foreign ministry says that China has sent a plane loaded with medical personnel and supplies to help with the fight against the spread of the coronavirus in the nation of 220 million people
content:
ISLAMABAD -- 
China has sent a plane loaded with medical personnel and supplies to aid Pakistan in the fight against the spread of the coronavirus in one of the world's most populous nations, the Pakistani foreign ministry said Saturday.
